200#define THROW_IF_SUSPENDED if (UNLIKELY(_page && _page->isSuspended())) \
201 [NSException raise:NSInternalInconsistencyException format:@"The WKWebView is suspended"]
202
203RetainPtr<NSError> nsErrorFromExceptionDetails(const WebCore::ExceptionDetails& details)
204{
205 auto userInfo = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
206
207 WKErrorCode errorCode;
208 switch (details.type) {
209 case WebCore::ExceptionDetails::Type::InvalidTargetFrame:
210 errorCode = WKErrorJavaScriptInvalidFrameTarget;
211 break;
212 case WebCore::ExceptionDetails::Type::Script:
213 errorCode = WKErrorJavaScriptExceptionOccurred;
214 break;
215 case WebCore::ExceptionDetails::Type::AppBoundDomain:
216 errorCode = WKErrorJavaScriptAppBoundDomain;
217 break;
218 }
219
220 [userInfo setObject:localizedDescriptionForErrorCode(errorCode) forKey:NSLocalizedDescriptionKey];
221 [userInfo setObject:details.message forKey:_WKJavaScriptExceptionMessageErrorKey];
222 [userInfo setObject:@(details.lineNumber) forKey:_WKJavaScriptExceptionLineNumberErrorKey];
223 [userInfo setObject:@(details.columnNumber) forKey:_WKJavaScriptExceptionColumnNumberErrorKey];
224
225 if (!details.sourceURL.isEmpty())
226 [userInfo setObject:[NSURL _web_URLWithWTFString:details.sourceURL] forKey:_WKJavaScriptExceptionSourceURLErrorKey];
227
228 return adoptNS([[NSError alloc] initWithDomain:WKErrorDomain code:errorCode userInfo:userInfo.get()]);
229}

231@implementation WKWebView

233- (instancetype)initWithFrame:(CGRect)frame
234{
235 return [self initWithFrame:frame configuration:adoptNS([[WKWebViewConfiguration alloc] init]).get()];
236}
237
238- (BOOL)_isValid
239{
240 return _page && _page->hasRunningProcess();
241}

245static bool shouldAllowPictureInPictureMediaPlayback()
246{
247 static bool shouldAllowPictureInPictureMediaPlayback = dyld_get_program_sdk_version() >= DYLD_IOS_VERSION_9_0;
248 return shouldAllowPictureInPictureMediaPlayback;
249}
250
251static bool shouldAllowSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs()
252{
253 static bool shouldAllowSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs = (WebCore::IOSApplication::isCardiogram() || WebCore::IOSApplication::isNike()) && !linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstThatDisallowsSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs);
254 return shouldAllowSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs;
255}
256
257#endif // PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)

259static bool shouldRequireUserGestureToLoadVideo()
260{
261#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
262 static bool shouldRequireUserGestureToLoadVideo = dyld_get_program_sdk_version() >= DYLD_IOS_VERSION_10_0;
263 return shouldRequireUserGestureToLoadVideo;
264#else
265 return false;
266#endif
267}
268
269static bool shouldRestrictBaseURLSchemes()
270{
271 static bool shouldRestrictBaseURLSchemes = linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstThatRestrictsBaseURLSchemes);
272 return shouldRestrictBaseURLSchemes;
273}

275#if PLATFORM(MAC)
276static uint32_t convertUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy(WKUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy policy)
277{
278 switch (policy) {
279 case WKUserInterfaceDirectionPolicyContent:
280 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceDirectionPolicy::Content);
281 case WKUserInterfaceDirectionPolicySystem:
282 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceDirectionPolicy::System);
283 }
284 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceDirectionPolicy::Content);
285}
286
287static uint32_t convertSystemLayoutDirection(NSUserInterfaceLayoutDirection direction)
288{
289 switch (direction) {
290 case NSUserInterfaceLayoutDirectionLeftToRight:
291 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceLayoutDirection::LTR);
292 case NSUserInterfaceLayoutDirectionRightToLeft:
293 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceLayoutDirection::RTL);
294 }
295 return static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceLayoutDirection::LTR);
296}
297
298#endif // PLATFORM(MAC)

300static void validate(WKWebViewConfiguration *configuration)
301{
302 if (!configuration.processPool)
303 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration.processPool is nil"];
304
305 if (!configuration.preferences)
306 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration.preferences is nil"];
307
308 if (!configuration.userContentController)
309 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration.userContentController is nil"];
310
311 if (!configuration.websiteDataStore)
312 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration.websiteDataStore is nil"];
313
314 if (!configuration._visitedLinkStore)
315 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration._visitedLinkStore is nil"];
316
317#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
318 if (!configuration._contentProviderRegistry)
319 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"configuration._contentProviderRegistry is nil"];
320#endif
321}
322
323#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
324static void hardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChangedCallback(CFNotificationCenterRef, void* observer, CFStringRef, const void*, CFDictionaryRef)
325{
326 ASSERT(observer);
327 WKWebView *webView = (__bridge WKWebView *)observer;
328 [webView->_contentView _hardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChanged];
329 webView._page->hardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChanged(GSEventIsHardwareKeyboardAttached());
330}
331#endif
332
333- (void)_initializeWithConfiguration:(WKWebViewConfiguration *)configuration
334{
335 if (!configuration)
336 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"Configuration cannot be nil"];
337
338 _configuration = adoptNS([configuration copy]);
339
340 if (WKWebView *relatedWebView = [_configuration _relatedWebView]) {
341 WKProcessPool *processPool = [_configuration processPool];
342 WKProcessPool *relatedWebViewProcessPool = [relatedWebView->_configuration processPool];
343 if (processPool && processPool != relatedWebViewProcessPool)
344 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"Related web view %@ has process pool %@ but configuration specifies a different process pool %@", relatedWebView, relatedWebViewProcessPool, configuration.processPool];
345 if ([relatedWebView->_configuration websiteDataStore] != [_configuration websiteDataStore] && linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWithExceptionsForRelatedWebViewsUsingDifferentDataStores, WebCore::AssumeSafariIsAlwaysLinkedOnAfter::No))
346 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"Related web view %@ has data store %@ but configuration specifies a different data store %@", relatedWebView, [relatedWebView->_configuration websiteDataStore], [_configuration websiteDataStore]];
347
348 [_configuration setProcessPool:relatedWebViewProcessPool];
349 }
350
351 validate(_configuration.get());
352
353 WebKit::WebProcessPool& processPool = *[_configuration processPool]->_processPool;
354
355 auto pageConfiguration = [configuration copyPageConfiguration];
356
357 pageConfiguration->setProcessPool(&processPool);
358
359 [self _setupPageConfiguration:pageConfiguration];
360
361 _usePlatformFindUI = YES;
362
363#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
364 _avoidsUnsafeArea = YES;
365 _obscuredInsetEdgesAffectedBySafeArea = UIRectEdgeTop | UIRectEdgeLeft | UIRectEdgeRight;
366 _viewportMetaTagWidth = WebCore::ViewportArguments::ValueAuto;
367 _initialScaleFactor = 1;
368 _allowsViewportShrinkToFit = defaultAllowsViewportShrinkToFit;
369
370 static uint32_t programSDKVersion = dyld_get_program_sdk_version();
371 _allowsLinkPreview = programSDKVersion >= firstSDKVersionWithLinkPreviewEnabledByDefault;
372
373 auto fastClickingEnabled = []() {
374 if (NSNumber *enabledValue = [[NSUserDefaults standardUserDefaults] objectForKey:@"WebKitFastClickingDisabled"])
375 return enabledValue.boolValue;
376 return defaultFastClickingEnabled;
377 };
378
379 _fastClickingIsDisabled = fastClickingEnabled();
380 _dragInteractionPolicy = _WKDragInteractionPolicyDefault;
381
382 _contentView = adoptNS([[WKContentView alloc] initWithFrame:self.bounds processPool:processPool configuration:pageConfiguration.copyRef() webView:self]);
383 _page = [_contentView page];
384 [[_configuration _contentProviderRegistry] addPage:*_page];
385
386 [self _setupScrollAndContentViews];
387 if (!self.opaque || !pageConfiguration->drawsBackground())
388 [self _setOpaqueInternal:NO];
389 else
390 [self _updateScrollViewBackground];
391
392 [self _frameOrBoundsChanged];
393 [self _registerForNotifications];
394
395 _page->contentSizeCategoryDidChange([self _contentSizeCategory]);
396
397 CFNotificationCenterAddObserver(CFNotificationCenterGetDarwinNotifyCenter(), (__bridge const void *)(self), hardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChangedCallback, (CFStringRef)[NSString stringWithUTF8String:kGSEventHardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChangedNotification], nullptr, CFNotificationSuspensionBehaviorCoalesce);
398#endif // PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
399
400#if ENABLE(META_VIEWPORT)
401 _page->setForceAlwaysUserScalable([_configuration ignoresViewportScaleLimits]);
402#endif
403
404#if PLATFORM(MAC)
405 _impl = makeUnique<WebKit::WebViewImpl>(self, self, processPool, pageConfiguration.copyRef());
406 _page = &_impl->page();
407
408 if (_impl->isUsingUISideCompositing())
409 _contentView = adoptNS([[WKContentView alloc] initWithFrame:self.bounds page:_page.copyRef()]);
410
411 _impl->setAutomaticallyAdjustsContentInsets(true);
412 _impl->setRequiresUserActionForEditingControlsManager([configuration _requiresUserActionForEditingControlsManager]);
413
414 [self _setupScrollAndContentViews];
415#endif
416
417 if (NSString *applicationNameForUserAgent = configuration.applicationNameForUserAgent)
418 _page->setApplicationNameForUserAgent(applicationNameForUserAgent);
419
420 _page->setApplicationNameForDesktopUserAgent(configuration._applicationNameForDesktopUserAgent);
421
422 _navigationState = makeUnique<WebKit::NavigationState>(self);
423 _page->setNavigationClient(_navigationState->createNavigationClient());
424
425 _uiDelegate = makeUnique<WebKit::UIDelegate>(self);
426 _page->setFindClient(makeUnique<WebKit::FindClient>(self));
427 _page->setDiagnosticLoggingClient(makeUnique<WebKit::DiagnosticLoggingClient>(self));
428
429 _iconLoadingDelegate = makeUnique<WebKit::IconLoadingDelegate>(self);
430 _resourceLoadDelegate = makeUnique<WebKit::ResourceLoadDelegate>(self);
431
432 for (auto& pair : pageConfiguration->urlSchemeHandlers())
433 _page->setURLSchemeHandlerForScheme(WebKit::WebURLSchemeHandlerCocoa::create(static_cast<WebKit::WebURLSchemeHandlerCocoa&>(pair.value.get()).apiHandler()), pair.key);
434
435 _page->setCocoaView(self);
436
437 [WebViewVisualIdentificationOverlay installForWebViewIfNeeded:self kind:@"WKWebView" deprecated:NO];
438
439#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
440 auto timeNow = MonotonicTime::now();
441 _timeOfRequestForVisibleContentRectUpdate = timeNow;
442 _timeOfLastVisibleContentRectUpdate = timeNow;
443 _timeOfFirstVisibleContentRectUpdateWithPendingCommit = timeNow;
444#endif
445}
446
447- (void)_setupPageConfiguration:(Ref<API::PageConfiguration>&)pageConfiguration
448{
449 pageConfiguration->setPreferences([_configuration preferences]->_preferences.get());
450 if (WKWebView *relatedWebView = [_configuration _relatedWebView])
451 pageConfiguration->setRelatedPage(relatedWebView->_page.get());
452
453 pageConfiguration->setUserContentController([_configuration userContentController]->_userContentControllerProxy.get());
454 pageConfiguration->setVisitedLinkStore([_configuration _visitedLinkStore]->_visitedLinkStore.get());
455 pageConfiguration->setWebsiteDataStore([_configuration websiteDataStore]->_websiteDataStore.get());
456 pageConfiguration->setDefaultWebsitePolicies([_configuration defaultWebpagePreferences]->_websitePolicies.get());
457
458#if PLATFORM(MAC)
459 if (auto pageGroup = WebKit::toImpl([_configuration _pageGroup]))
460 pageConfiguration->setPageGroup(pageGroup);
461 else
462#endif
463 {
464 NSString *groupIdentifier = [_configuration _groupIdentifier];
465 if (groupIdentifier.length)
466 pageConfiguration->setPageGroup(WebKit::WebPageGroup::create(groupIdentifier).ptr());
467 }
468
469 pageConfiguration->setAdditionalSupportedImageTypes(makeVector<String>([_configuration _additionalSupportedImageTypes]));
470
471 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSuppressesIncrementalRendering(!![_configuration suppressesIncrementalRendering]);
472
473 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldRespectImageOrientation(!![_configuration _respectsImageOrientation]);
474#if !PLATFORM(MAC)
475 // FIXME: Expose WKPreferences._shouldPrintBackgrounds on iOS, adopt it in all iOS clients, and remove this and WKWebViewConfiguration._printsBackgrounds.
476 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldPrintBackgrounds(!![_configuration _printsBackgrounds]);
477#endif
478 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setIncrementalRenderingSuppressionTimeout([_configuration _incrementalRenderingSuppressionTimeout]);
479 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setJavaScriptMarkupEnabled(!![_configuration _allowsJavaScriptMarkup]);
480 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldConvertPositionStyleOnCopy(!![_configuration _convertsPositionStyleOnCopy]);
481 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setHTTPEquivEnabled(!![_configuration _allowsMetaRefresh]);
482 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowUniversalAccessFromFileURLs(!![_configuration _allowUniversalAccessFromFileURLs]);
483 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowTopNavigationToDataURLs(!![_configuration _allowTopNavigationToDataURLs]);
484 pageConfiguration->setWaitsForPaintAfterViewDidMoveToWindow([_configuration _waitsForPaintAfterViewDidMoveToWindow]);
485 pageConfiguration->setDrawsBackground([_configuration _drawsBackground]);
486 pageConfiguration->setControlledByAutomation([_configuration _isControlledByAutomation]);
487 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setIncompleteImageBorderEnabled(!![_configuration _incompleteImageBorderEnabled]);
488 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldDeferAsynchronousScriptsUntilAfterDocumentLoadOrFirstPaint(!![_configuration _shouldDeferAsynchronousScriptsUntilAfterDocumentLoad]);
489 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldRestrictBaseURLSchemes(shouldRestrictBaseURLSchemes());
490
491#if PLATFORM(MAC)
492 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShowsURLsInToolTipsEnabled(!![_configuration _showsURLsInToolTips]);
493 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setServiceControlsEnabled(!![_configuration _serviceControlsEnabled]);
494
495 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy(convertUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy([_configuration userInterfaceDirectionPolicy]));
496 // We are in the View's initialization routine, so our client hasn't had time to set our user interface direction.
497 // Therefore, according to the docs[1], "this property contains the value reported by the app's userInterfaceLayoutDirection property."
498 // [1] http://developer.apple.com/library/mac/documentation/Cocoa/Reference/ApplicationKit/Classes/NSView_Class/index.html#//apple_ref/doc/uid/20000014-SW222
499 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSystemLayoutDirection(convertSystemLayoutDirection(self.userInterfaceLayoutDirection));
500#endif
501
502#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
503 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowsInlineMediaPlayback(!![_configuration allowsInlineMediaPlayback]);
504 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowsInlineMediaPlaybackAfterFullscreen(!![_configuration _allowsInlineMediaPlaybackAfterFullscreen]);
505 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setInlineMediaPlaybackRequiresPlaysInlineAttribute(!![_configuration _inlineMediaPlaybackRequiresPlaysInlineAttribute]);
506 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowsPictureInPictureMediaPlayback(!![_configuration allowsPictureInPictureMediaPlayback] && shouldAllowPictureInPictureMediaPlayback());
507 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setUserInterfaceDirectionPolicy(static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::UserInterfaceDirectionPolicy::Content));
508 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSystemLayoutDirection(static_cast<uint32_t>(WebCore::TextDirection::LTR));
509 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs(shouldAllowSettingAnyXHRHeaderFromFileURLs());
510 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setShouldDecidePolicyBeforeLoadingQuickLookPreview(!![_configuration _shouldDecidePolicyBeforeLoadingQuickLookPreview]);
511#if ENABLE(DEVICE_ORIENTATION)
512 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setDeviceOrientationPermissionAPIEnabled(linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWithDeviceOrientationAndMotionPermissionAPI));
513#endif
514#if USE(SYSTEM_PREVIEW)
515 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSystemPreviewEnabled(!![_configuration _systemPreviewEnabled]);
516#endif
517#endif // PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
518
519 WKAudiovisualMediaTypes mediaTypesRequiringUserGesture = [_configuration mediaTypesRequiringUserActionForPlayback];
520 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setRequiresUserGestureForVideoPlayback((mediaTypesRequiringUserGesture & WKAudiovisualMediaTypeVideo) == WKAudiovisualMediaTypeVideo);
521 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setRequiresUserGestureForAudioPlayback(((mediaTypesRequiringUserGesture & WKAudiovisualMediaTypeAudio) == WKAudiovisualMediaTypeAudio));
522 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setRequiresUserGestureToLoadVideo(shouldRequireUserGestureToLoadVideo());
523 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setMainContentUserGestureOverrideEnabled(!![_configuration _mainContentUserGestureOverrideEnabled]);
524 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setInvisibleAutoplayNotPermitted(!![_configuration _invisibleAutoplayNotPermitted]);
525 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setMediaDataLoadsAutomatically(!![_configuration _mediaDataLoadsAutomatically]);
526 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAttachmentElementEnabled(!![_configuration _attachmentElementEnabled]);
527
528#if ENABLE(DATA_DETECTION) && PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
529 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setDataDetectorTypes(static_cast<uint32_t>(fromWKDataDetectorTypes([_configuration dataDetectorTypes])));
530#endif
531#if ENABLE(WIRELESS_PLAYBACK_TARGET)
532 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowsAirPlayForMediaPlayback(!![_configuration allowsAirPlayForMediaPlayback]);
533#endif
534
535#if ENABLE(APPLE_PAY)
536 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setApplePayEnabled(!![_configuration _applePayEnabled]);
537#endif
538
539 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setNeedsStorageAccessFromFileURLsQuirk(!![_configuration _needsStorageAccessFromFileURLsQuirk]);
540 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setMediaContentTypesRequiringHardwareSupport(String([_configuration _mediaContentTypesRequiringHardwareSupport]));
541 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAllowMediaContentTypesRequiringHardwareSupportAsFallback(!![_configuration _allowMediaContentTypesRequiringHardwareSupportAsFallback]);
542 if (!pageConfiguration->preferences()->mediaDevicesEnabled())
543 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setMediaDevicesEnabled(!![_configuration _mediaCaptureEnabled]);
544
545 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setColorFilterEnabled(!![_configuration _colorFilterEnabled]);
546
547 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setUndoManagerAPIEnabled(!![_configuration _undoManagerAPIEnabled]);
548
549#if ENABLE(APP_HIGHLIGHTS)
550 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setAppHighlightsEnabled(!![_configuration _appHighlightsEnabled]);
551#endif
552

554 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setLegacyEncryptedMediaAPIEnabled(!![_configuration _legacyEncryptedMediaAPIEnabled]);
555#endif

557#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY) && ENABLE(SERVICE_WORKER)
558 bool hasServiceWorkerEntitlement = (WTF::processHasEntitlement("com.apple.developer.WebKit.ServiceWorkers") || WTF::processHasEntitlement("com.apple.developer.web-browser")) && ![_configuration preferences]._serviceWorkerEntitlementDisabledForTesting;

562#endif

564 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSampledPageTopColorMaxDifference([_configuration _sampledPageTopColorMaxDifference]);
565 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setSampledPageTopColorMinHeight([_configuration _sampledPageTopColorMinHeight]);
566
567 if (!linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWhereSiteSpecificQuirksAreEnabledByDefault))
568 pageConfiguration->preferences()->setNeedsSiteSpecificQuirks(false);
569}

618{

620 return;
621
622#if PLATFORM(MAC)
623 [_textFinderClient willDestroyView:self];
624#endif
625
626#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
627 [_contentView _webViewDestroyed];
628
629 if (_page && _remoteObjectRegistry)
630 _page->process().processPool().removeMessageReceiver(Messages::RemoteObjectRegistry::messageReceiverName(), _page->identifier());
631#endif
632
633 if (_page)
634 _page->close();
635
636#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)

638 [[_configuration _contentProviderRegistry] removePage:*_page];
639 [[NSNotificationCenter defaultCenter] removeObserver:self];
640 [_scrollView setInternalDelegate:nil];
641
642 CFNotificationCenterRemoveObserver(CFNotificationCenterGetDarwinNotifyCenter(), (__bridge const void *)(self), (CFStringRef)[NSString stringWithUTF8String:kGSEventHardwareKeyboardAvailabilityChangedNotification], nullptr);
643#endif
644
645 [super dealloc];
646}

763- (void)resumeDownloadFromResumeData:(NSData *)resumeData completionHandler:(void(^)(WKDownload *))completionHandler
764{
765 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
766 auto unarchiver = adoptNS([[NSKeyedUnarchiver alloc] initForReadingFromData:resumeData error:nil]);
767 [unarchiver setDecodingFailurePolicy:NSDecodingFailurePolicyRaiseException];
768 NSDictionary *dictionary = [unarchiver decodeObjectOfClasses:[NSSet setWithObjects:[NSDictionary class], [NSArray class], [NSString class], [NSNumber class], [NSData class], [NSURL class], [NSURLRequest class], nil] forKey:@"NSKeyedArchiveRootObjectKey"];
769 [unarchiver finishDecoding];
770 NSString *path = [dictionary objectForKey:@"NSURLSessionResumeInfoLocalPath"];
771
772 if (!path)
773 [NSException raise:NSInvalidArgumentException format:@"Invalid resume data"];
774
775#if USE(LEGACY_CFNETWORK_DOWNLOADS)
776 // Mojave CFNetwork fails to resume a download if the destination does not exist.
777 // If someone has removed the destination file, make an empty file at that location.
778 if (![[NSFileManager defaultManager] fileExistsAtPath:path])
779 [[NSData data] writeToFile:path atomically:YES];
780#endif
781
782 _page->resumeDownload(API::Data::createWithoutCopying(resumeData), path, [completionHandler = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)] (auto* download) {
783 if (download)
784 completionHandler(wrapper(download));
785 else
786 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
787 });
788}

903static bool validateArgument(id argument)
904{
905 if ([argument isKindOfClass:[NSString class]] || [argument isKindOfClass:[NSNumber class]] || [argument isKindOfClass:[NSDate class]] || [argument isKindOfClass:[NSNull class]])
906 return true;
907
908 if ([argument isKindOfClass:[NSArray class]]) {
909 __block BOOL valid = true;
910
911 [argument enumerateObjectsUsingBlock:^(id object, NSUInteger, BOOL *stop) {
912 if (!validateArgument(object)) {
913 valid = false;
914 *stop = YES;
915 }
916 }];
917
918 return valid;
919 }
920
921 if ([argument isKindOfClass:[NSDictionary class]]) {
922 __block bool valid = true;
923
924 [argument enumerateKeysAndObjectsUsingBlock:^(id key, id value, BOOL *stop) {
925 if (!validateArgument(key) || !validateArgument(value)) {
926 valid = false;
927 *stop = YES;
928 }
929 }];
930
931 return valid;
932 }
933
934 return false;
935}

998static WKMediaPlaybackState toWKMediaPlaybackState(WebKit::MediaPlaybackState mediaPlaybackState)
999{
1000 switch (mediaPlaybackState) {
1001 case WebKit::MediaPlaybackState::NoMediaPlayback:
1002 return WKMediaPlaybackStateNone;
1003 case WebKit::MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackPlaying:
1004 return WKMediaPlaybackStatePlaying;
1005 case WebKit::MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackPaused:
1006 return WKMediaPlaybackStatePaused;
1007 case WebKit::MediaPlaybackState::MediaPlaybackSuspended:
1008 return WKMediaPlaybackStateSuspended;
1009 default:
1010 break;
1011 }
1012 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1013 return WKMediaPlaybackStateNone;
1014}

1096- (void)_evaluateJavaScript:(NSString *)javaScriptString asAsyncFunction:(BOOL)asAsyncFunction withSourceURL:(NSURL *)sourceURL withArguments:(NSDictionary<NSString *, id> *)arguments forceUserGesture:(BOOL)forceUserGesture inFrame:(WKFrameInfo *)frame inWorld:(WKContentWorld *)world completionHandler:(void (^)(id, NSError *))completionHandler
1097{
1098 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
1099 auto handler = adoptNS([completionHandler copy]);
1100
1101 std::optional<WebCore::ArgumentWireBytesMap> argumentsMap;
1102 if (asAsyncFunction)
1103 argumentsMap = WebCore::ArgumentWireBytesMap { };
1104 NSString *errorMessage = nil;
1105
1106 for (id key in arguments) {
1107 id value = [arguments objectForKey:key];
1108 auto serializedValue = API::SerializedScriptValue::createFromNSObject(value);
1109 if (!serializedValue) {
1110 errorMessage = @"Function argument values must be one of the following types, or contain only the following types: NSNumber, NSNull, NSDate, NSString, NSArray, and NSDictionary";
1111 break;
1112 }
1113
1114 argumentsMap->set(key, serializedValue->internalRepresentation().toWireBytes());
1115 }
1116
1117 if (errorMessage && handler) {
1118 RetainPtr<NSMutableDictionary> userInfo = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] init]);
1119
1120 [userInfo setObject:localizedDescriptionForErrorCode(WKErrorJavaScriptExceptionOccurred) forKey:NSLocalizedDescriptionKey];
1121 [userInfo setObject:errorMessage forKey:_WKJavaScriptExceptionMessageErrorKey];
1122
1123 auto error = adoptNS([[NSError alloc] initWithDomain:WKErrorDomain code:WKErrorJavaScriptExceptionOccurred userInfo:userInfo.get()]);
1124 RunLoop::main().dispatch([handler, error] {
1125 auto rawHandler = (void (^)(id, NSError *))handler.get();
1126 rawHandler(nil, error.get());
1127 });
1128
1129 return;
1130 }
1131
1132 std::optional<WebCore::FrameIdentifier> frameID;
1133 if (frame) {
1134 if (uint64_t identifier = frame._handle.frameID)
1135 frameID = makeObjectIdentifier<WebCore::FrameIdentifierType>(identifier);
1136 }
1137
1138 _page->runJavaScriptInFrameInScriptWorld({ javaScriptString, sourceURL, !!asAsyncFunction, WTFMove(argumentsMap), !!forceUserGesture }, frameID, *world->_contentWorld.get(), [handler] (auto&& result) {
1139 if (!handler)
1140 return;
1141
1142 auto rawHandler = (void (^)(id, NSError *))handler.get();
1143 if (!result.has_value()) {
1144 rawHandler(nil, nsErrorFromExceptionDetails(result.error()).get());
1145 return;
1146 }
1147
1148 if (!result.value()) {
1149 rawHandler(nil, createNSError(WKErrorJavaScriptResultTypeIsUnsupported).get());
1150 return;
1151 }
1152
1153 id body = API::SerializedScriptValue::deserialize(result.value()->internalRepresentation(), 0);
1154 rawHandler(body, nil);
1155 });
1156}
1157
1158- (void)takeSnapshotWithConfiguration:(WKSnapshotConfiguration *)snapshotConfiguration completionHandler:(void(^)(CocoaImage *, NSError *))completionHandler
1159{
1160 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
1161 constexpr bool snapshotFailedTraceValue = false;
1162 tracePoint(TakeSnapshotStart);
1163
1164 CGRect rectInViewCoordinates = snapshotConfiguration && !CGRectIsNull(snapshotConfiguration.rect) ? snapshotConfiguration.rect : self.bounds;
1165 CGFloat snapshotWidth;
1166 if (snapshotConfiguration)
1167 snapshotWidth = snapshotConfiguration.snapshotWidth.doubleValue ?: rectInViewCoordinates.size.width;
1168 else
1169 snapshotWidth = self.bounds.size.width;
1170
1171 auto handler = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler);
1172
1173 if (CGRectIsEmpty(rectInViewCoordinates) || !snapshotWidth) {
1174 RunLoop::main().dispatch([completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)]() mutable {
1175#if USE(APPKIT)
1176 auto image = adoptNS([[NSImage alloc] initWithSize:NSMakeSize(0, 0)]);
1177#else
1178 auto image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] init]);
1179#endif
1180 completionHandler(image.get(), nil);
1181 });
1182 return;
1183 }
1184
1185#if USE(APPKIT)
1186 CGFloat imageScale = snapshotWidth / rectInViewCoordinates.size.width;
1187 CGFloat imageHeight = imageScale * rectInViewCoordinates.size.height;
1188
1189 // Need to scale by device scale factor or the image will be distorted.
1190 CGFloat deviceScale = _page->deviceScaleFactor();
1191 WebCore::IntSize bitmapSize(snapshotWidth, imageHeight);
1192 bitmapSize.scale(deviceScale, deviceScale);
1193
1194 // Software snapshot will not capture elements rendered with hardware acceleration (WebGL, video, etc).
1195 // This code doesn't consider snapshotConfiguration.afterScreenUpdates since the software snapshot always
1196 // contains recent updates. If we ever have a UI-side snapshot mechanism on macOS, we will need to factor
1197 // in snapshotConfiguration.afterScreenUpdates at that time.
1198 _page->takeSnapshot(WebCore::enclosingIntRect(rectInViewCoordinates), bitmapSize, WebKit::SnapshotOptionsInViewCoordinates, [handler, snapshotWidth, imageHeight](const WebKit::ShareableBitmap::Handle& imageHandle) {
1199 if (imageHandle.isNull()) {
1200 tracePoint(TakeSnapshotEnd, snapshotFailedTraceValue);
1201 handler(nil, createNSError(WKErrorUnknown).get());
1202 return;
1203 }
1204 auto bitmap = WebKit::ShareableBitmap::create(imageHandle, WebKit::SharedMemory::Protection::ReadOnly);
1205 RetainPtr<CGImageRef> cgImage = bitmap ? bitmap->makeCGImage() : nullptr;
1206 auto image = adoptNS([[NSImage alloc] initWithCGImage:cgImage.get() size:NSMakeSize(snapshotWidth, imageHeight)]);
1207 tracePoint(TakeSnapshotEnd, true);
1208 handler(image.get(), nil);
1209 });
1210#else
1211 CGFloat deviceScale = _page->deviceScaleFactor();
1212 RetainPtr<WKWebView> strongSelf = self;
1213 auto callSnapshotRect = [strongSelf, rectInViewCoordinates, snapshotWidth, deviceScale, handler] {
1214 [strongSelf _snapshotRect:rectInViewCoordinates intoImageOfWidth:(snapshotWidth * deviceScale) completionHandler:[strongSelf, handler, deviceScale](CGImageRef snapshotImage) {
1215 RetainPtr<NSError> error;
1216 RetainPtr<UIImage> image;
1217
1218 if (!snapshotImage)
1219 error = createNSError(WKErrorUnknown);
1220 else
1221 image = adoptNS([[UIImage alloc] initWithCGImage:snapshotImage scale:deviceScale orientation:UIImageOrientationUp]);
1222
1223 tracePoint(TakeSnapshotEnd, !!snapshotImage);
1224 handler(image.get(), error.get());
1225 }];
1226 };
1227
1228 if ((snapshotConfiguration && !snapshotConfiguration.afterScreenUpdates) || !linkedOnOrAfter(WebCore::SDKVersion::FirstWithSnapshotAfterScreenUpdates)) {
1229 callSnapshotRect();
1230 return;
1231 }
1232
1233 _page->callAfterNextPresentationUpdate([callSnapshotRect = WTFMove(callSnapshotRect), handler](WebKit::CallbackBase::Error error) mutable {
1234 if (error != WebKit::CallbackBase::Error::None) {
1235 tracePoint(TakeSnapshotEnd, snapshotFailedTraceValue);
1236 handler(nil, createNSError(WKErrorUnknown).get());
1237 return;
1238 }
1239
1240 // Create an implicit transaction to ensure a commit will happen next.
1241 [CATransaction activate];
1242
1243 // Wait for the next flush to ensure the latest IOSurfaces are pushed to backboardd before taking the snapshot.
1244 [CATransaction addCommitHandler:[callSnapshotRect = WTFMove(callSnapshotRect)]() mutable {
1245 // callSnapshotRect() calls the client callback which may call directly or indirectly addCommitHandler.
1246 // It is prohibited by CA to add a commit handler while processing a registered commit handler.
1247 // So postpone calling callSnapshotRect() till CATransaction processes its commit handlers.
1248 dispatch_async(dispatch_get_main_queue(), [callSnapshotRect = WTFMove(callSnapshotRect)] {
1249 callSnapshotRect();
1250 });
1251 } forPhase:kCATransactionPhasePostCommit];
1252 });
1253#endif
1254}

1343inline OptionSet<WebKit::FindOptions> toFindOptions(WKFindConfiguration *configuration)
1344{

1349 if (configuration.backwards)

1456- (void)_showSafeBrowsingWarning:(const WebKit::SafeBrowsingWarning&)warning completionHandler:(CompletionHandler<void(Variant<WebKit::ContinueUnsafeLoad, URL>&&)>&&)completionHandler
1457{
1458 _safeBrowsingWarning = adoptNS([[WKSafeBrowsingWarning alloc] initWithFrame:self.bounds safeBrowsingWarning:warning completionHandler:[weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKWebView>(self), completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)] (auto&& result) mutable {
1459 completionHandler(WTFMove(result));
1460 auto strongSelf = weakSelf.get();
1461 if (!strongSelf)
1462 return;
1463 bool navigatesFrame = WTF::switchOn(result,
1464 [] (WebKit::ContinueUnsafeLoad continueUnsafeLoad) { return continueUnsafeLoad == WebKit::ContinueUnsafeLoad::Yes; },
1465 [] (const URL&) { return true; }
1466 );
1467 bool forMainFrameNavigation = [strongSelf->_safeBrowsingWarning forMainFrameNavigation];
1468 if (navigatesFrame && forMainFrameNavigation) {
1469 // The safe browsing warning will be hidden once the next page is shown.
1470 return;
1471 }
1472 if (!navigatesFrame && strongSelf->_safeBrowsingWarning && !forMainFrameNavigation) {
1473 strongSelf->_page->goBack();
1474 return;
1475 }
1476 [std::exchange(strongSelf->_safeBrowsingWarning, nullptr) removeFromSuperview];
1477 }]);
1478 [self addSubview:_safeBrowsingWarning.get()];
1479}
1480
1481- (void)_clearSafeBrowsingWarning
1482{
1483 [std::exchange(_safeBrowsingWarning, nullptr) removeFromSuperview];
1484}
1485
1486- (void)_clearSafeBrowsingWarningIfForMainFrameNavigation
1487{
1488 if ([_safeBrowsingWarning forMainFrameNavigation])
1489 [self _clearSafeBrowsingWarning];
1490}

1492- (void)_internalDoAfterNextPresentationUpdate:(void (^)(void))updateBlock withoutWaitingForPainting:(BOOL)withoutWaitingForPainting withoutWaitingForAnimatedResize:(BOOL)withoutWaitingForAnimatedResize
1493{
1494#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1495 if (![self usesStandardContentView]) {
1496 RunLoop::main().dispatch([updateBlock = makeBlockPtr(updateBlock)] {
1497 updateBlock();
1498 });
1499 return;
1500 }
1501#endif
1502
1503 if (withoutWaitingForPainting)
1504 _page->setShouldSkipWaitingForPaintAfterNextViewDidMoveToWindow(true);
1505
1506 auto updateBlockCopy = makeBlockPtr(updateBlock);
1507
1508 RetainPtr<WKWebView> strongSelf = self;
1509 _page->callAfterNextPresentationUpdate([updateBlockCopy, withoutWaitingForAnimatedResize, strongSelf](WebKit::CallbackBase::Error error) {
1510 if (!updateBlockCopy)
1511 return;
1512
1513#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1514 if (!withoutWaitingForAnimatedResize && strongSelf->_dynamicViewportUpdateMode != WebKit::DynamicViewportUpdateMode::NotResizing) {
1515 strongSelf->_callbacksDeferredDuringResize.append([updateBlockCopy] {
1516 updateBlockCopy();
1517 });
1518
1519 return;
1520 }
1521#else
1522 UNUSED_PARAM(withoutWaitingForAnimatedResize);
1523#endif
1524
1525 updateBlockCopy();
1526 });
1527}

1613- (void)createPDFWithConfiguration:(WKPDFConfiguration *)pdfConfiguration completionHandler:(void (^)(NSData *pdfDocumentData, NSError *error))completionHandler
1614{
1615 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
1616 WebCore::FrameIdentifier frameID;
1617 if (auto mainFrame = _page->mainFrame())
1618 frameID = mainFrame->frameID();
1619 else {
1620 completionHandler(nil, createNSError(WKErrorUnknown).get());
1621 return;
1622 }
1623
1624 std::optional<WebCore::FloatRect> floatRect;
1625 if (pdfConfiguration && !CGRectIsNull(pdfConfiguration.rect))
1626 floatRect = WebCore::FloatRect(pdfConfiguration.rect);
1627
1628 _page->drawToPDF(frameID, floatRect, [handler = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)](const IPC::DataReference& pdfData) {
1629 if (pdfData.isEmpty()) {
1630 handler(nil, createNSError(WKErrorUnknown).get());
1631 return;
1632 }
1633
1634 auto data = adoptCF(CFDataCreate(kCFAllocatorDefault, pdfData.data(), pdfData.size()));
1635 handler((NSData *)data.get(), nil);
1636 });
1637}

1647static NSDictionary *dictionaryRepresentationForEditorState(const WebKit::EditorState& state)
1648{
1649 if (state.isMissingPostLayoutData)
1650 return @{ @"post-layout-data" : @NO };
1651
1652 auto& postLayoutData = state.postLayoutData();
1653 return @{
1654 @"post-layout-data" : @YES,
1655 @"bold": postLayoutData.typingAttributes & WebKit::AttributeBold ? @YES : @NO,
1656 @"italic": postLayoutData.typingAttributes & WebKit::AttributeItalics ? @YES : @NO,
1657 @"underline": postLayoutData.typingAttributes & WebKit::AttributeUnderline ? @YES : @NO,
1658 @"text-alignment": @(nsTextAlignment(static_cast<WebKit::TextAlignment>(postLayoutData.textAlignment))),
1659 @"text-color": (NSString *)serializationForCSS(postLayoutData.textColor)
1660 };
1661}
1662
1663static NSTextAlignment nsTextAlignment(WebKit::TextAlignment alignment)
1664{
1665 switch (alignment) {
1666 case WebKit::NoAlignment:
1667 return NSTextAlignmentNatural;
1668 case WebKit::LeftAlignment:
1669 return NSTextAlignmentLeft;
1670 case WebKit::RightAlignment:
1671 return NSTextAlignmentRight;
1672 case WebKit::CenterAlignment:
1673 return NSTextAlignmentCenter;
1674 case WebKit::JustifiedAlignment:
1675 return NSTextAlignmentJustified;
1676 }
1677 ASSERT_NOT_REACHED();
1678 return NSTextAlignmentNatural;
1679}
1680
1681static _WKSelectionAttributes selectionAttributes(const WebKit::EditorState& editorState, _WKSelectionAttributes previousAttributes)
1682{
1683 _WKSelectionAttributes attributes = _WKSelectionAttributeNoSelection;
1684 if (editorState.selectionIsNone)
1685 return attributes;
1686
1687 if (editorState.selectionIsRange)
1688 attributes |= _WKSelectionAttributeIsRange;
1689 else
1690 attributes |= _WKSelectionAttributeIsCaret;
1691
1692 if (!editorState.isMissingPostLayoutData) {
1693#if PLATFORM(IOS_FAMILY)
1694 if (editorState.postLayoutData().atStartOfSentence)
1695 attributes |= _WKSelectionAttributeAtStartOfSentence;
1696#endif
1697 } else if (previousAttributes & _WKSelectionAttributeAtStartOfSentence)
1698 attributes |= _WKSelectionAttributeAtStartOfSentence;
1699
1700 return attributes;
1701}
1702
1703- (void)_didChangeEditorState
1704{
1705 auto newSelectionAttributes = selectionAttributes(_page->editorState(), _selectionAttributes);
1706 if (_selectionAttributes != newSelectionAttributes) {
1707 NSString *selectionAttributesKey = NSStringFromSelector(@selector(_selectionAttributes));
1708 [self willChangeValueForKey:selectionAttributesKey];
1709 _selectionAttributes = newSelectionAttributes;
1710 [self didChangeValueForKey:selectionAttributesKey];
1711 }
1712
1713 // FIXME: We should either rename -_webView:editorStateDidChange: to clarify that it's only intended for use when testing,
1714 // or remove it entirely and use -_webView:didChangeFontAttributes: instead once text alignment is supported in the set of
1715 // font attributes.
1716 id <WKUIDelegatePrivate> uiDelegate = (id <WKUIDelegatePrivate>)self.UIDelegate;
1717 if ([uiDelegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:editorStateDidChange:)])
1718 [uiDelegate _webView:self editorStateDidChange:dictionaryRepresentationForEditorState(_page->editorState())];
1719}

2003static RetainPtr<NSDictionary<NSString *, id>> createUserInfo(const std::optional<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationTokenInfo>& info)
2004{
2005 if (!info)
2006 return { };
2007
2008 auto result = adoptNS([[NSMutableDictionary alloc] initWithCapacity:3]);
2009 if (!info->documentURL.isNull())
2010 [result setObject:(NSURL *)info->documentURL forKey:_WKTextManipulationTokenUserInfoDocumentURLKey];
2011 if (!info->tagName.isNull())
2012 [result setObject:(NSString *)info->tagName forKey:_WKTextManipulationTokenUserInfoTagNameKey];
2013 if (!info->roleAttribute.isNull())
2014 [result setObject:(NSString *)info->roleAttribute forKey:_WKTextManipulationTokenUserInfoRoleAttributeKey];
2015 [result setObject:@(info->isVisible) forKey:_WKTextManipulationTokenUserInfoVisibilityKey];
2016
2017 return result;
2018}

2020- (void)_startTextManipulationsWithConfiguration:(_WKTextManipulationConfiguration *)configuration completion:(void(^)())completionHandler
2021{
2022 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
2023 using ExclusionRule = WebCore::TextManipulationController::ExclusionRule;
2024
2025 if (!_textManipulationDelegate || !_page) {
2026 completionHandler();
2027 return;
2028 }
2029
2030 Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ExclusionRule> exclusionRules;
2031 if (configuration) {
2032 for (_WKTextManipulationExclusionRule *wkRule in configuration.exclusionRules) {
2033 auto type = wkRule.isExclusion ? ExclusionRule::Type::Exclude : ExclusionRule::Type::Include;
2034 if (wkRule.attributeName)
2035 exclusionRules.append({type, ExclusionRule::AttributeRule { wkRule.attributeName, wkRule.attributeValue } });
2036 else if (wkRule.className)
2037 exclusionRules.append({type, ExclusionRule::ClassRule { wkRule.className } });
2038 else
2039 exclusionRules.append({type, ExclusionRule::ElementRule { wkRule.elementName } });
2040 }
2041 }
2042
2043 _page->startTextManipulations(exclusionRules, [weakSelf = WeakObjCPtr<WKWebView>(self)] (const Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem>& itemReferences) {
2044 if (!weakSelf)
2045 return;
2046
2047 auto retainedSelf = weakSelf.get();
2048 auto delegate = [retainedSelf _textManipulationDelegate];
2049 if (!delegate)
2050 return;
2051
2052 auto createWKItem = [] (const WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem& item) {
2053 auto tokens = createNSArray(item.tokens, [] (auto& token) {
2054 auto wkToken = adoptNS([[_WKTextManipulationToken alloc] init]);
2055 [wkToken setIdentifier:String::number(token.identifier.toUInt64())];
2056 [wkToken setContent:token.content];
2057 [wkToken setExcluded:token.isExcluded];
2058 [wkToken setUserInfo:createUserInfo(token.info).get()];
2059 return wkToken;
2060 });
2061 return adoptNS([[_WKTextManipulationItem alloc] initWithIdentifier:String::number(item.identifier.toUInt64()) tokens:tokens.get()]);
2062 };
2063
2064 if ([delegate respondsToSelector:@selector(_webView:didFindTextManipulationItems:)])
2065 [delegate _webView:retainedSelf.get() didFindTextManipulationItems:createNSArray(itemReferences, createWKItem).get()];
2066 else {
2067 for (auto& item : itemReferences)
2068 [delegate _webView:retainedSelf.get() didFindTextManipulationItem:createWKItem(item).get()];
2069 }
2070 }, [capturedCompletionBlock = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)] () {
2071 capturedCompletionBlock();
2072 });
2073}

2075static WebCore::TextManipulationController::ItemIdentifier coreTextManipulationItemIdentifierFromString(NSString *identifier)
2076{
2077 return makeObjectIdentifier<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ItemIdentifierType>(identifier.longLongValue);
2078}
2079
2080static WebCore::TextManipulationController::TokenIdentifier coreTextManipulationTokenIdentifierFromString(NSString *identifier)
2081{
2082 return makeObjectIdentifier<WebCore::TextManipulationController::TokenIdentifierType>(identifier.longLongValue);
2083}

2085- (void)_completeTextManipulation:(_WKTextManipulationItem *)item completion:(void(^)(BOOL success))completionHandler
2086{
2087 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
2088 if (!_page) {
2089 completionHandler(false);
2090 return;
2091 }
2092
2093 auto itemID = coreTextManipulationItemIdentifierFromString(item.identifier);
2094
2095 Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationToken> tokens;
2096 for (_WKTextManipulationToken *wkToken in item.tokens)
2097 tokens.append(WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationToken { coreTextManipulationTokenIdentifierFromString(wkToken.identifier), wkToken.content, std::nullopt });
2098
2099 Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem> coreItems;
2100 coreItems.reserveInitialCapacity(1);
2101 coreItems.uncheckedAppend(WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem { itemID, WTFMove(tokens) });
2102 _page->completeTextManipulation(coreItems, [capturedCompletionBlock = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)] (bool allFailed, auto& failures) {
2103 capturedCompletionBlock(!allFailed && failures.isEmpty());
2104 });
2105}
2106
2107static RetainPtr<NSMutableArray> makeFailureSetForAllTextManipulationItems(NSArray<_WKTextManipulationItem *> *items)
2108{
2109 RetainPtr<NSMutableArray> wkFailures = adoptNS([[NSMutableArray alloc] initWithCapacity:items.count]);
2110 for (_WKTextManipulationItem *item in items)
2111 [wkFailures addObject:[NSError errorWithDomain:_WKTextManipulationItemErrorDomain code:_WKTextManipulationItemErrorNotAvailable userInfo:@{_WKTextManipulationItemErrorItemKey: item}]];
2112 return wkFailures;
2113};
2114
2115static RetainPtr<NSArray> wkTextManipulationErrors(NSArray<_WKTextManipulationItem *> *items, const Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationFailure>& failures)
2116{
2117 if (failures.isEmpty())
2118 return nil;
2119
2120 return createNSArray(failures, [&] (auto& coreFailure) -> NSError * {
2121 ASSERT(coreFailure.index < items.count);
2122 if (coreFailure.index >= items.count)
2123 return nil;
2124 auto errorCode = static_cast<NSInteger>(([&coreFailure] {
2125 using Type = WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationFailureType;
2126 switch (coreFailure.type) {
2127 case Type::ContentChanged:
2128 return _WKTextManipulationItemErrorContentChanged;
2129 case Type::InvalidItem:
2130 return _WKTextManipulationItemErrorInvalidItem;
2131 case Type::InvalidToken:
2132 return _WKTextManipulationItemErrorInvalidToken;
2133 case Type::ExclusionViolation:
2134 return _WKTextManipulationItemErrorExclusionViolation;
2135 }
2136 })());
2137 auto item = items[coreFailure.index];
2138 ASSERT(coreTextManipulationItemIdentifierFromString(item.identifier) == coreFailure.identifier);
2139 return [NSError errorWithDomain:_WKTextManipulationItemErrorDomain code:errorCode userInfo:@{_WKTextManipulationItemErrorItemKey: item}];
2140 });
2141}
2142
2143- (void)_completeTextManipulationForItems:(NSArray<_WKTextManipulationItem *> *)items completion:(void(^)(NSArray<NSError *> *errors))completionHandler
2144{
2145 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
2146 if (!_page) {
2147 completionHandler(makeFailureSetForAllTextManipulationItems(items).get());
2148 return;
2149 }
2150
2151 Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem> coreItems;
2152 coreItems.reserveInitialCapacity(items.count);
2153 for (_WKTextManipulationItem *wkItem in items) {
2154 Vector<WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationToken> coreTokens;
2155 coreTokens.reserveInitialCapacity(wkItem.tokens.count);
2156 for (_WKTextManipulationToken *wkToken in wkItem.tokens)
2157 coreTokens.uncheckedAppend(WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationToken { coreTextManipulationTokenIdentifierFromString(wkToken.identifier), wkToken.content, std::nullopt });
2158 coreItems.uncheckedAppend(WebCore::TextManipulationController::ManipulationItem { coreTextManipulationItemIdentifierFromString(wkItem.identifier), WTFMove(coreTokens) });
2159 }
2160
2161 RetainPtr<NSArray<_WKTextManipulationItem *>> retainedItems = items;
2162 _page->completeTextManipulation(coreItems, [capturedItems = retainedItems, capturedCompletionBlock = makeBlockPtr(completionHandler)](bool allFailed, auto& failures) {
2163 if (allFailed) {
2164 capturedCompletionBlock(makeFailureSetForAllTextManipulationItems(capturedItems.get()).get());
2165 return;
2166 }
2167 capturedCompletionBlock(wkTextManipulationErrors(capturedItems.get(), failures).get());
2168 });
2169}

2380- (WKNavigation *)_loadRequest:(NSURLRequest *)request shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy:(_WKShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy)shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy
2381{
2382 THROW_IF_SUSPENDED;
2383 WebCore::ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy policy;
2384 switch (shouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy) {
2385 case _WKShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicyNotAllow:
2386 policy = WebCore::ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy::ShouldNotAllow;
2387 break;
2388 case _WKShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicyAllow:
2389 policy = WebCore::ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy::ShouldAllow;
2390 break;
2391 case _WKShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicyAllowExternalSchemesButNotAppLinks:
2392 policy = WebCore::ShouldOpenExternalURLsPolicy::ShouldAllowExternalSchemesButNotAppLinks;
2393 break;
2394 }
2395 return wrapper(_page->loadRequest(request, policy));

2901static inline OptionSet<WebCore::LayoutMilestone> layoutMilestones(_WKRenderingProgressEvents events)
2902{
2903 OptionSet<WebCore::LayoutMilestone> milestones;
2904
2905 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstLayout)
2906 milestones.add(WebCore::DidFirstLayout);
2907
2908 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout)
2909 milestones.add(WebCore::DidFirstVisuallyNonEmptyLayout);
2910
2911 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstPaintWithSignificantArea)
2912 milestones.add(WebCore::DidHitRelevantRepaintedObjectsAreaThreshold);
2913
2914 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventReachedSessionRestorationRenderTreeSizeThreshold)
2915 milestones.add(WebCore::ReachedSessionRestorationRenderTreeSizeThreshold);
2916
2917 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstLayoutAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering)
2918 milestones.add(WebCore::DidFirstLayoutAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering);
2919
2920 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstPaintAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering)
2921 milestones.add(WebCore::DidFirstPaintAfterSuppressedIncrementalRendering);
2922
2923 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventDidRenderSignificantAmountOfText)
2924 milestones.add(WebCore::DidRenderSignificantAmountOfText);
2925
2926 if (events & _WKRenderingProgressEventFirstMeaningfulPaint)
2927 milestones.add(WebCore::DidFirstMeaningfulPaint);
2928
2929 return milestones;
2930}
2931
2932- (void)_setObservedRenderingProgressEvents:(_WKRenderingProgressEvents)observedRenderingProgressEvents
2933{
2934 _observedRenderingProgressEvents = observedRenderingProgressEvents;
2935 _page->listenForLayoutMilestones(layoutMilestones(observedRenderingProgressEvents));
2936}

3148static inline OptionSet<WebKit::FindOptions> toFindOptions(_WKFindOptions wkFindOptions)
3149{
3150 OptionSet<WebKit::FindOptions> findOptions;
3151
3152 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsCaseInsensitive)
3153 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::CaseInsensitive);
3154 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsAtWordStarts)
3155 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::AtWordStarts);
3156 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsTreatMedialCapitalAsWordStart)
3157 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::TreatMedialCapitalAsWordStart);
3158 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsBackwards)
3159 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::Backwards);
3160 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsWrapAround)
3161 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::WrapAround);
3162 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsShowOverlay)
3163 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::ShowOverlay);
3164 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsShowFindIndicator)
3165 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::ShowFindIndicator);
3166 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsShowHighlight)
3167 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::ShowHighlight);
3168 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsNoIndexChange)
3169 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::NoIndexChange);
3170 if (wkFindOptions & _WKFindOptionsDetermineMatchIndex)
3171 findOptions.add(WebKit::FindOptions::DetermineMatchIndex);
3172
3173 return findOptions;
3174}
